#CHIP YM2413
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2413 (OPLL) Built-in Patches Test
;
; The YM2413 has 16 built-in patches (preset voices) plus a custom patch mode.
; This test validates all 16 built-in patches by playing a simple melody
; with each patch to verify correct voice selection.
;
; Test sequence: Play each of the 16 patches with a C4 note

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Patch 0: User patch (default) - we'll use this as baseline
@0 c4 .

; Patch 1: Violin
@1 c4 .

; Patch 2: Guitar
@2 c4 .

; Patch 3: Piano
@3 c4 .

; Patch 4: Flute
@4 c4 .

; Patch 5: Clarinet
@5 c4 .

; Patch 6: Trumpet
@6 c4 .

; Patch 7: Organ
@7 c4 .

r4

; Patch 8: Horn
@8 c4 .

; Patch 9: Synth
@9 c4 .

; Patch 10: Harpsichord
@10 c4 .

; Patch 11: Vibraphone
@11 c4 .

; Patch 12: Synth Bass
@12 c4 .

; Patch 13: Wood Bass
@13 c4 .

r4

; Patch 14: Electric Guitar
@14 c4 .

; Patch 15: Synth Strings
@15 c4 .

; Patch 16: Piano 2 (actually index 15 in some implementations)
; Note: OPLL has 15 preset patches + 1 user patch = 16 total
; Using patch 0 again to verify it hasn't changed
@0 c4 .

r2

#END
